    "category": "edu-podcast",
    "podcastUrl": "https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/1FvkHvjvIEw4Ti0nOSIHhc?utm_source=generator",
    "content": "\n\t\t\n<p>In this episode, Bledi Taska, Executive Vice President and Chief Economist at Lightcast, explores the future of remote work and its profound impact on productivity and talent acquisition.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Join José ‘Pepe’ Escamilla, the Associate Director of IFE, as he delves into this enlightening conversation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>A podcast presented by Tec Sounds.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n                <div class=\"tags\">\n                            <a href=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/edu-news/tag/future-of-work/ \" rel=\"tag\">future of work</a>\n                            <a href=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/edu-news/tag/remote-work/ \" rel=\"tag\">remote work</a>\n                    </div>\n        <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <a class=\"author-link\" href=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/edu-news/author/joseescamilla/\" rel=\"author\">\n                <div class=\"avatar\">\n                    <img src=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Foto_Jose-Escamilla-150x150.jpg\">                </div>\n                <div class=\"author\">\n                    <strong>Jose Escamilla</strong> \n                </div>\n            </a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"share-box\">\n                            <span>Share</span>\n                        <button id=\"fbShareBtn\" class=\"share-button\">\n  <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"shareOnFacebook('https%3A%2F%2Fobservatory.tec.mx%2Fedutrends-podcast-episode%2Fep-46-the-enduring-era-of-remote-work-a-conversation-with-bledi-task%2F')\">\n    <img class=\"observatorio-logo\" src=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/wp-content/themes/observatorio-tec/assets/img/icons/facebook.png\" alt=\"facebook\">\n  </a>\n</button>\n\n<script>\n  function shareOnFacebook(url) {\n    window.open('https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=' + url, 'Facebook Share', 'width=600,height=400');\n  }\n</script>\n\n            <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/share?text=Ep. 46 – The Enduring Era of Remote Work: A Conversation with Bledi Task&amp;url=\" id=\"twShareBtn\" class=\"share-button\"><img class=\"observatorio-logo\" src=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/wp-content/themes/observatorio-tec/assets/img/icons/twitter.png')\" alt=\"twitter\"></a>\n            <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https://observatory.tec.mx/edutrends-podcast-episode/ep-46-the-enduring-era-of-remote-work-a-conversation-with-bledi-task/\" id=\"liShareBtn\" class=\"share-button\"><img class=\"observatorio-logo\" src=\"https://observatory.tec.mx/wp-content/themes/observatorio-tec/assets/img/icons/linkedin.png')\" alt=\"linkedin\"></a>\n        </div>\n\n\n    <p class=\"notecc\">This article from <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.es \">Observatory of the Institute for the Future of Education</a> may be shared under the terms of the license CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 <img class=\"imgcc\" src=\"https://observatorio.tec.mx/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cc.png\"></p>\t",
